This script will show you certain days that either had a gain or drop of a certain percent and highlight that day and 4 days after.
The strategy is to long/short on the next day and then close the position x number of days later.

Input:
- Long or Short
- Down Day or Up Day
- Percent of Change day changed (up or down from previous input)
- Number of days until you close the position
